        "cooked": "<p>All Tilde servers have internet connectivity. You can use them as a proxy servers to circumvent censorship, but please do not abuse the link as all the servers are run by the volunteers and are not intended to be used for torrenting etc.</p>\n<p>The simpliest setup is Socks5 server using OpenSSH: <code>ssh -D 1080 servername.example.com</code></p>\n<p>In Russia, you can use it with <a href=\"https://ntc.party/c/community-software/runet-censorship-bypass-extension\">Runet Censorship Bypass</a> browser extension by <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/ilyaigpetrov\">@ilyaigpetrov</a>, it has support for Socks5 proxies.</p>",
